    section.row-fluid.summary
      .summary.span3
        h3 WITH
        p.lead Piped queries
      .details.span9
        p
          | The 
          code WITH
          |  clause allows queries to be chained together, piping the results from one
          | to be used as starting points or criteria in the next.
        table.table-condensed.table-help
          tr
            th Reference:
            td
              a(href='http://docs.neo4j.org/chunked/{{neo4j.version}}/query-with.html')
                code.icon-external-link-sign &nbsp;WITH
              |  manual page
          tr
            th Related:
            td
              a(help-topic='match') :help MATCH
              | &nbsp;
              a(help-topic='return') :help RETURN
              | &nbsp;
              a(help-topic='cypher') :help Cypher
    section.row-fluid.example
      .span9.offset3
        figure
          pre.code(mode='cypher').
            MATCH (director:Person)-[:DIRECTED]->(movie)
            WITH director, ORDER BY count(movie.title) LIMIT 1
              MATCH (director)<-[:KNOWS*..6]-(hopeful)
              WHERE hopeful.name = "Starlet Ohuru"
          figcaption Find a path from a hopeful actor to Hollywood's most prolific director.

